 <refsect1 role="examples">
  &reftitle.examples;
  <para>
  下面的例子给出了一种去除所有输出缓冲区的方法：   
  </para>
  <para>
   <example>
    <title><function>ob_end_clean</function> example</title>
    <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php
ob_start();
echo 'Text that won\'t get displayed.';
ob_end_clean();
?>
]]>
    </programlisting>
   </example>
  </para>
 </refsect1>

